_sText:
I was bored, saw a cute map, had an idea and came up with this. Small map, 12 spawns for each team, everyone starts with an usp, m4a1, kevlar and a knife. No buy zones.

------------
INSTALLATION:
------------

Put the files here:
...\Steam\SteamApps\"your account"\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

Download, Comment, etc. Enjoy.



[]  Nemus Monachus
